      "span_text": "To check the validity of these variables, we related them to a well-known typology of alcohol dependence, namely Early (EOA) (≤25 years) or Late Onset Alcoholism (LOA) (N25 years) with more evidence of familial alcoholism for EOA [CITATION_1] ."
